where the aliphatic and cycloaliphatic moieties in the radicals R10 may be party or fully halogenated and/or may carry 1, 2 or 3 substituents selected from OH, CN, C1-C4-alkoxy, C1-C4-haloalkoxy, C1-C4-alkylthio and C1-C4-haloalkylthio, where the cycloaliphatic moieties may also carry 1, 2 or 3 C1-C6-alkyl substituents,

