where the aromatic and heterocyclic moieties in the radicals R15 may be partly or fully halogenated and/or may carry 1, 2, 3, 4 or 5 substituents selected from OH, CN, C1-C6-alkyl, C1-C6-haloalkyl, C1-C4-alkoxy, C1-C4-haloalkoxy, C1-C4-alkylthio, C1-C4-haloalkylthio, C1-C4-alkylcarbonyl, C1-C4-haloalkylcarbonyl, C1-C4-alkylsulfonyl and C1-C4-haloalkylsulfonyl; andmis 0, 1 or 2;
